The problem is in the `vertical-align` attribute of `.fa-layers`.

We have `-.125em` in `.svg-inline--fa` and `-12.5%` in `.fa-layers`.

Workaround:
```css
.fa-layers {
  vertical-align: -.125em;
}
```

I'm labeling this as bug, but I don't know if there are other side effects of doing that

